Subject: [PATCH 2/4] phone-controller Slice 4: combo HID device
 (keyboard+gamepad+media), controller UI, release signing

- :hid-core (new pure-JVM module): combo descriptor (3 reports), KeyboardState/
  GamepadState builders, kernel-convention gamepad bits, D-pad->hat combine; 16 tests.
- Transport: registers the combo device; hold-capable key/gamepad/dpad/media APIs;
  connect-to-bonded; all-release on disconnect/stop; SecurityException surfaced.
- MainActivity + ControllerPads: runtime BT permissions, live verdict/status,
  Discoverable + Connect actions, three hold-capable pads. No AndroidX.
- app/build.gradle.kts: v0.4.0 (versionCode 2) + env-driven release signing
  (PC_RELEASE_* vars; debug-signing fallback keeps assembleRelease installable).
- READMEs: download/install/pair/emulator-mapping path (product) + module/report/
  signing map (android).

